<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̉ḥly̱ ạsm nrnm byh</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̉ḥly̱ ạsm nrnm byh bnqwlh ạ̉w bngẖnyh
 yạ yswʿ ạsmk trnym sẖʿbk .. ạ̉ḥly̱ mạ ʿndh wạ̉gẖly̱ mạ lyh
 ạ̉ḥly̱ ạsm nrnm byh
 ạlqrạr- yswʿ yswʿ .. yswʿ yswʿ
 ạsmk ʿạly ḥlw wgẖạly .. ʿly̱ qlb ạlsẖʿb ạlly fạdyh
 (ạ̉ḥly̱ ạsm nrnm byh)2
 2- ạsmk brj ḥṣyn ntmnʿ .. fyh ḥmạytnạ bnjry ạ̹lyh
 ạsmk bynạ ʿẓym ntmtʿ .. nkrm sẖkẖṣk wnʿlyh
 ạ̉ḥly̱ ạsm nrnm byh
 3- ạsm jlạlk yfḍl lynạ .. rạyẗ nṣrẗ wʿznạ byh
 ʿạrfyn ạsmk kl ṭryqnạ .. hw njạtnạ wgẖạlbyn byh
 ạ̉ḥly̱ ạsm nrnm byh
 4- hạnsbḥ whạndẖkr ạsmk .. bạlrwḥ nfrḥ bmʿạnyh
 ḥwạlyk ntjmʿ tbạrknạ .. wtnsynạ ạlly nʿạnyh
 ạ̉ḥly̱ ạsm nrnm byh</lyrics>
